6:
It's no use, he's starting to
regenerate again!
9:
Stella! You need to gain control of
the Lance! You are its original
bearer...
11:
If you break the barrier around the
Lance, I can use it to slay the
daemon! Do it now!
26: Now, Stella, while we have a chance!
30:
By the will of the Stars, I order you.
Return to your rightful owner!
39:
Amalgamation of spite and malice,
UNRAVEL!
42:
Ilbis... You are not fit to bear the
power of the curse. That burden
shall fall to me.
53:
Aaagh... Kill... KILL YOU...
ALL... I MUST...
60:
Don't you remember, Camir? As
Rolan lay there dying, he turned to
me and he...
63:
...He asked me to FORGIVE you for
what you had done. Because he
didn't want me to be consumed by
a grudge.
78:
Hahaha... How pathetic. Did you
actually think he'd come around?
That he could be saved?
80:
It's no use. People like him... People
like me... We're broken! Defective,
incapable of understanding your
kind.
89:
Why did you have to go... and do all
of this?! What's the point of it all?!
92:
Those eyes... Is that pity? Why are
you looking at me like that? I don't
need your PITY!
96:
Tell me... That little refugee runt...
Why was he bawling his tiny little
eyes out, exactly?
100:
He never gave me a proper answer.
Was probably too busy crying over
his mother's corpse!
110:
I thought I told you... DON'T GIVE ME
THAT LOOK!
119:
I suppose this is the only way I can
take down foes in this form... By
catching them unawares.
125:
Don't worry about me. As Champion,
I had to slay countless fiends. I am
used to this.
127:
...I suppose this will now enable us to
travel to the surface?
128:
Let us go. It's time for our journey to
come to an end.
